Model averaged predictions for CCME Boron Data

Source: R/data.R
boron_pred.Rd

A data frame of the predictions based on 1,000 bootstrap iterations.

boron_pred

Format

A tbl data frame:

percent

The percent of species affected <int>.

est

The estimated concentration <dbl>.

se

The standard error of the estimate <dbl>.

lcl

The lower confidence limit <dbl>.

se

The upper confidence limit <dbl>.

dist

The distribution <chr>.

Examples

head(boron_pred)
#> # A tibble: 6 x 6
#>   percent   est    se   lcl   ucl dist   
#>     <int> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl> <chr>  
#> 1       1 0.379 0.361 0.125  1.46 average
#> 2       2 0.624 0.507 0.217  2.11 average
#> 3       3 0.856 0.621 0.317  2.65 average
#> 4       4 1.08  0.720 0.422  3.15 average
#> 5       5 1.31  0.808 0.527  3.57 average
#> 6       6 1.53  0.889 0.637  4.00 average
